    "The present survey, however, will focus on the narrower, but now commercially important, subfield of Deep Learning (DL) in Artificial Neural.",
    "III.Natural Language Processing: Natural language processing (NLP) is a computer system that analyzes and understands human languages like English, Japanese, Italian, or Russian.",
    "It can interpret text, build databases, generate summaries, or maintain user dialogues.",
    "This article focuses on issues in natural language comprehension and generation from text or keyboard input, aiming to improve database and information retrieval capabilities.",
    "IV.Computer Vision in Biological Context: This book explores the neuroscientific study of neuronal computations in the visual cortex, the psychological understanding of visual cognition, and the burgeoning field of biologically inspired artificial intelligence [17]."
